    <content>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;html lang=en-us&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta http-equiv=X-UA-Compatible content="IE=edge"&gt;&lt;meta http-equiv=content-type content="text/html; charset=utf-8"&gt;&lt;meta name=viewport content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1"&gt;&lt;title&gt;Introduction &amp;middot; Static Site&lt;/title&gt;&lt;link href=//assets/styles/styles-b11a9815c966b8090aeab5ca5472bc67.css rel=stylesheet type=text/css /&gt;&lt;link rel=apple-touch-icon-precomposed sizes=144x144 href=//assets/images/apple-touch-icon-precomposed.png&gt;&lt;link rel="shortcut icon" href=//assets/images/apple-touch-icon-precomposed.png&gt;&lt;link rel=alternate type=application/rss+xml title=RSS href=//atom.xml&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;nav&gt;&lt;a href=// &gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=//about&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/nav&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a href=// title=Home&gt;Static Site&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;Static site generator utilizing Gulp and Metalsmith&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="container content"&gt;&lt;div class=post&gt;&lt;h1 class=post-title&gt;Introduction&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;span class=post-date&gt;Mon May 01 2017 12:00:00 GMT-0400 (Eastern Daylight Time)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p&gt;Static Site Generator based on&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=http://www.metalsmith.io/ &gt;Metalsmith&lt;/a&gt; - an extremely simple, pluggable static site generator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=http://gulpjs.com/ &gt;Gulp v4&lt;/a&gt; - the streaming build system For those well acquainted with &lt;a href=http://jekyllrb.com/ &gt;Jekyll&lt;/a&gt;, folder structure and naming convention of posts will be familiar.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id=features&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This site generator includes the following features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=https://www.browsersync.io/ &gt;Browsersync&lt;/a&gt; - time-saving synchronised browser testing (once you go live-reload, you&amp;#39;ll never come back)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=http://sass-lang.com/ &gt;Sass&lt;/a&gt; - CSS with superpowers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=https://github.com/postcss/postcss&gt;PostCSS&lt;/a&gt; - a tool for transforming styles with JS plugins&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer&gt;Autoprefixer&lt;/a&gt; - adding vendor prefixes by the rules of &lt;a href=http://caniuse.com/ &gt;Can I Use&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=http://eslint.org/ &gt;ESLint&lt;/a&gt; - the pluggable linting utility for JavaScript and JSX (with preconfigured ruleset by &lt;a href=https://github.com/google/eslint-config-google&gt;Google&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=https://github.com/leizongmin/tinyliquid&gt;Liquid&lt;/a&gt; - an awesome, Django/Jinja-like template engine for node.js (similar to Jekyll&amp;#39;s &lt;a href=http://shopify.github.io/liquid/ &gt;Liquid&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;copy; All rights reserved.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script src=//assets/scripts/scripts-8d9ac681d4a07f95d19fd62342e2d465.js&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</content>
